com.google.api.gax.grpc

Class ClientContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.gax.grpc.ClientContext

  • @BetaApi
public abstract class ClientContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates client state, including channel, executor, and credentials.

    Unlike ClientSettings which allows users to configure the client, ClientContext is intended to be used in generated code. Most users will not need to use it.
